66
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:06,400
Bratře Yi Huai!

67
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,900
Yi Huai!

68
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:10,500
Prober se.

69
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:17,100
Otče, je mi jedno, jestli chceš království Dong Yue ukrást,

70
00:06:17,100 --> 00:06:20,400
